headline: What Vanguard and Robinhood Have in Common Might Surprise You
summary: At first glance, Vanguard and  Robinhood  don’t appear to have much in common.  Robinhood is buying TradePMR, a custodian for independent financial advisors, and is preparing to launch an AI-powered financial advice offering next year.  Vanguard, meanwhile, created a new advice and wealth management division and hired former Fidelity executive Joanna Rotenberg to lead it.
